original: Lagergren, Lars Rudolf Alfred, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 5/4/01 i Gbg av kamr. John L. o. Anna Lagergrén. G. 38 m. Maria (Maja) Grönwall. Barn: Margareta. — Stud:ex. v. Gbgs h. latin 20, med. stud. v. Upps. univ. 21-23, tandl:kand. 26, tandl. 36. Stud. i Kiel 30-31, genomg. därvid operationskurs. Vik. i Svenljunga 36, prakt, i Gbg sed. 36. Hobby: motorsport.
translated: Lagergren, Lars Rudolf Alfred, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 5/4/01 in Gothenburg, son of the late John L. and Anna Lagergrén. Married in 1938 to Maria (Maja) Grönwall. Children: Margareta. — Completed high school education at Gothenburg's Latin School in 1920, studied medicine at Uppsala University from 1921-1923, graduated with a dental degree in 1926, became a licensed dentist in 1936. Continued studies in Kiel from 1930-1931, including completing an operations course. Temporary dentist in Svenljunga in 1936, practicing in Gothenburg since 1936. Hobby: motorsports.
